\f2\b Google Document AI
\f1\b0 : best first-pass document OCR/HTR for your messy logbooks\
	\'95	
\f2\b AWS Textract
\f1\b0 : useful fallback / second opinion\
	\'95	
\f2\b OpenAI
\f1\b0 : best for structured extraction, correction suggestions, question answering, summarization, and semantic retrieval\
	\'95	
\f2\b OpenSearch / Elasticsearch
\f1\b0 : best for exact and auditable search behavior\
	\'95	
\f2\b Human review UI
\f1\b0 : non-negotiable\
